{"tid":1397382,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"應承我 不被捕 可唔可以？","createTime":"2019-08-02T12:29:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T12:39:07.000Z","uid":61886,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0c8a3637544543d56d8a70ce6e473bd037e23c6b","tid":1397382,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T12:29:05.000Z","msg":"今日有朋友買左啲物資比前線<br />\n全部都係靚裝<br />\n我會聽日後日拎上前線比戰友<br />\n<br />\n傾開計 講開水炮車<br />\n佢同我講<br />\n「如果你係前面，一定要捉走學生」<br />\n我話<br />\n「我會 我唔想任何一個手足出事」<br />\n<br />\n可唔可以應承我<br />\n聽日後日大後日<br />\n都要「不被捕」<br />\n可以嗎？"},{"pid":"4c74a55d377a99a197a36c74bb1c29b657dd3935","tid":1397382,"uid":61886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T12:32:27.000Z","msg":"我尊重前線決定<br />\n我自己都係前線<br />\n但逼不得已<br />\n我只會學71立法會義士咁<br />\n抬你地走"},{"pid":"7d4767c472bdfdf1e66efa5ae7183f67579b3cbe","tid":1397382,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T12:36:13.000Z","msg":"你夠唔夠力"},{"pid":"5dd6dad0d65030f5bb72528d85170357c40df51c","tid":1397382,"uid":93908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T12:37:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"669efd1359614b5ccd632a20f07c0627c8527b74","tid":1397382,"uid":160268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T12:38:42.000Z","msg":"留名睇樓主即刻被捕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea174047463a7a3eeeda66a48ed954296180a153","tid":1397382,"uid":262545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T12:39:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JBWnxHy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJBWnxHy.png&h=1ff65539&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QcT5vud.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQcT5vud.png&h=529c7b94&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hWGe8fU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.